{"tha-ap185:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap185:0.2":"Kutajapupphiyavagga ","tha-ap185:0.3":"3 Kotumbariyattheraapadana ","tha-ap185:1.1":"“Kanikaramva jotantam, ","tha-ap185:1.2":"nisinnam pabbatantare; ","tha-ap185:1.3":"Appameyyamva udadhim, ","tha-ap185:1.4":"vitthatam dharanim yatha. ","tha-ap185:2.1":"Pujitam devasanghena, ","tha-ap185:2.2":"nisabhajaniyam yatha; ","tha-ap185:2.3":"Hattho hatthena cittena, ","tha-ap185:2.4":"upagacchim naruttamam. ","tha-ap185:3.1":"Sattapupphani paggayha, ","tha-ap185:3.2":"kotumbarasamakulam; ","tha-ap185:3.3":"Buddhassa abhiropesim, ","tha-ap185:3.4":"sikhino lokabandhuno. ","tha-ap185:4.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap185:4.2":"yam pupphamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap185:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap185:4.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap185:5.1":"Ito visatikappamhi, ","tha-ap185:5.2":"mahanelasanamako; ","tha-ap185:5.3":"Eko asi mahatejo, ","tha-ap185:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap185:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap185:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap185:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap185:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma kotumbariyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap185:8.1":"Kotumbariyattherassapadanam tatiyam. "}